Singapore,Metro,Rapid,Transit,is,a,service,that,provides,information,on,Singapore,s,Metro,Transit,such,as,trains,buses,taxis,and,tourist,attractions,The,SMRT,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,and,data,of,SMRT,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,bus,arrival,times,retrieving,timetables,and,accessing,bus,service,information